{"title":"Clindamicina","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/Clindamicina-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Clindamicina","guid":"EIuxLw6pRRnDNNACwCZXaQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Uso y Dosis:","guid":"Et6Swelfn9cjyvw1kgJfuQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• ↓Actividad contra Bacteroides fragilis (resistencia mundial ≈ 60%) ⟶ No recomendado para infecciones intraabdominales (1).","guid":"Dvh2citjqdRBIRyyyAKsAw","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• Activo contra ≈ 80% de Clostridium, Peptostreptococcus, y Fusobacterium (variación geográfica en susceptibilidad) (1).","guid":"Vyr7bP2cyHpYOMbR3jluyg","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"• Sin actividad vs. enterococci, H. influenzae, y N. meningitidis (1).","guid":"JrwwNXlpuvQTu0cDrERWDA","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"• Profilaxis quirúrgica (operaciones nasales, orales, sinusales/faríngeas) ⟶ Preferido sobre metronidazol para infecciones anaeróbicas de cabeza, cuello y pulmón (1).","guid":"8yWLX5WeNrkqWjML9TwUFg","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"• Versátil: abarca bacterias aerobias y anaerobias, Pneumocystis, malaria, y Toxoplasma (1).","guid":"9S4gn4KRWExBpKIstdA-mA","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"• Inhibe síntesis de toxinas en síndrome de choque tóxico (1).","guid":"0LYARjSR_flY2ATQcPNZCQ","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"• Usos\\Nclínicos:","guid":"JMhc_w_1xJ-LErYv9xyQJQ","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"• Combinado con ciprofloxacino: ántrax.","guid":"mMsfiQaBu8lfS-LTdil8_w","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"• Combinado con quinina: malaria por P. falciparum, babesiosis.","guid":"YZeqPykNBjzsc8cVH1ADzg","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"• Combinado con primaquina: Pneumocystis.","guid":"rPN72SAYAJKgK19Vo2ZNfQ","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"8","text":"• Combinado con pirimetamina: toxoplasmosis cerebral.","guid":"oJljmDKue8VdIdF1QrpCWg","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"8","text":"• Infecciones por cocos gram (+) aerobios, incl. CA-MRSA (algunos con resistencia inducible).","guid":"A8pbblNpqEFiEOC42CrPqQ","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"8","text":"• Infecciones anaeróbicas en cabeza, cuello y pulmón.","guid":"yFeJviCFVYGSrG0CeqKeyw","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"8","text":"• Terapia tópica combinada para acné vulgaris leve/moderado (1).","guid":"tSqz59az7saTBDMMxPNahQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"0","text":"Dosis\\NAdultos:","guid":"4s9fsAci8lXANs21wevGyg","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"• Vía Oral: 150-450 mg c/6-8h (máx. 1.8 g/día).","guid":"bZido1hVrfNIsi8bQQphLg","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"• IV/IM: 1.2-2.7 g/día div. en 3 dosis (máx. 4.8 g/día). Infusión máx. 30 mg/min,\\Nconcentración final <18 mg/ml. No administrar >1200 mg en una infusión de 1h (1).","guid":"jUumr1eJBxStfHVwzNac7w","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"• Acné: Preparado tópico bid.","guid":"fggrst1_92GpQmhtfTzIuQ","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"16","text":"• Amnionitis, orofacial, espacio parafaríngeo: 600-900 mg IV c/8h.","guid":"80EekT9QQprD9vDANtAeHw","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"16","text":"• Ántrax: 900 mg IV c/8h (con ciprofloxacino o doxiciclina).","guid":"mb7JBGnSEEgn5OkkWo9Uzw","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"16","text":"• Vaginosis bacteriana: 1 supositorio vaginal/día hs x3 días,\\No 1 aplicador de gel vaginal 2% (Xaciato) x1 dosis (1).","guid":"-os4e2Jv4qzNDbZZ2hdpjQ","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"16","text":"• Supresión de toxinas: 900 mg IV c/8h.","guid":"2YIyA39LuTu3H37pLChjmA","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"0","text":"Ajuste Renal:","guid":"L8ChqMaMBi6kpN8DAlSYAA","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"• No requiere ajuste en insuficiencia renal (1).","guid":"CFCtiycjGIbsJMRRkhJdnw","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"0","text":"Ajuste Hepático:","guid":"hfq4nzeW2c790_4_buz8HA","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• No se requiere reducción en insuficiencia hepática leve/moderada.\\NConsiderar reducción en casos severos (1).","guid":"8nrjZ_eiOBznbIkI9sGkfQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"0","text":"Efectos\\NAdversos:","guid":"3Pm_7EC7NQnmmmoiAI4G1g","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"• Reacciones alérgicas: rash, fiebre, eritema multiforme, anafilaxia (1).","guid":"QyYGAVDzZ8RguwlJ5j6w9w","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"• ↑AST/ALT reversible. Rara progresión a lesión hepática severa (1).","guid":"5_djdlMk1xP0nectnN2nDg","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"• Colitis mediada por toxina de C. difficile y diarrea no mediada por toxina (1).","guid":"LTpwsgJLBxYu8ocha8DTpg","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"28","text":"• Otros: flebitis local, enfermedad del suero, náuseas/vómitos, cefalea,\\Ndisritmias (raro), neutropenia reversible, trombocitopenia, eosinofilia (1).","guid":"6S0iYG2xfnj2VvkpPlIT-Q","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"28","text":"• Alteración del gusto, lesión esofágica (1).","guid":"ZXXTt9OyClxpLVyi0XCFVA","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"0","text":"Riesgo en\\NEmbarazo:","guid":"AjrxaUF8Yqjc4JO7GpSdcA","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• Categoría 1: Sin evidencia de toxicidad en 2º/3º trimestre. Datos insuficientes en 1º trimestre (1).","guid":"Gb6JICAiyvzqjbO8-Qkozw","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"• Lactancia: Evitar si es posible, monitorear toxicidad GI en el infante si se usa (1).","guid":"zel45diELQj_1zGho40MxQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"0","text":"Espectro\\NAntimicrobiano","guid":"Kc85GiKKCpAySZgM0zILkg","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"RECOMENDADO ++ (3)","guid":"Jam-D0siRXW6MRao4oNRSA","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• Actinomyces sp.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"• Arcanobacter sp.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"• Capnocytophaga sp.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"37","text":"ACTIVO + (15)","guid":"S6-2jqeOyLwu-vVinWdHcQ","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• C. diphtheriae","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"• Clostridium sp.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"• F. necrophorum","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"• Peptostreptococci","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"42","text":"• Prevotella sp.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"42","text":"• S. aureus MSSA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"42","text":"• S. epidermidis (MS)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"42","text":"• S. lugdunensis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"42","text":"• S. saprophyticus","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"42","text":"• Staph coag-neg (MS)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"42","text":"• Strep. agalactiae gp (B)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"42","text":"• Strep. anginosus gp","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"42","text":"• Strep. gp C, F, G","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"42","text":"• Strep. pneumoniae","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"42","text":"• Strep. pyogenes gp (A)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"0","text":"Farmacología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"• Índice PK/PD: AUC/MIC en 24 h.","guid":"SuOnhPkDYos-TlcEMqAGJA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"• Preparaciones farmacéuticas: Cápsulas (75, 150, 300 mg), soln oral (75 mg/5 mL),\\Ntópico (gel, crema, loción), supositorio vaginal, gel vaginal, inyección.","guid":"QORk5Ir0hv64SpUOn1Q-Nw","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"• Absorción oral (%): 90%.","guid":"Yc-cL9frG3WRwaKDB5fRQg","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"58","text":"• Tmax (h): 0.75.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"58","text":"• Conc. sérica máxima\\N(µg/mL):","guid":"yE4IpAoAdZBpiy6vs8GcUQ","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"• 2.5 (150 mg po, dosis única).","guid":"4MaiSGOQ9ZIkXCjLNiwBdw","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"• 14.1 (900 mg IV c/8h, estado estacionario).","guid":"UvaqxOUUnj8NgONNdb7m3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"58","text":"• Unión a proteínas (%): 85-94%.","guid":"ZcBrtukFnpwWCuAsaqaScw","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"58","text":"• Volumen de distribución (Vd): 1.1 L/kg.","guid":"eUUmJBXsgL5GYwUt-LZyDw","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"58","text":"• T½ sérico promedio (h): 2.4.","guid":"JCPFd5rRRMcZBGwFZJEJDA","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"58","text":"• Eliminación: Metabolizado.","guid":"Nx87AH9Tjq55FOaANoejTg","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"58","text":"• Penetración biliar (%): 250-300%.","guid":"2JDkHhqIfi6JsIGJRtlfLg","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"58","text":"• Penetración LCR/sangre (%): No datos disponibles.","guid":"SBfeimsIxV9iVpIrYsl9aQ","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"58","text":"• Niveles terapéuticos en LCR: No.","guid":"BaYB_dsvOfAeEzwkl3houw","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"0","text":"Interacciones Enzimáticas y\\Ncon Transportadores","guid":"","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"• Sustrato de CYP450: 3A4.","guid":"gAX9MigFo4TMo33vnHEW0w","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"• Interacciones con transportadores: No especificado.","guid":"vYtzYBwwFY1F3OgU0EzkgQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"• Inhibición/inducción de CYP450 y transportadores: No especificado.","guid":"A1Ka2L0-ODfB08a_7hXPpw","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"• Impacto en conc. de\\Nfármacos en suero:","guid":"_lvMUIll-y7tu8FPmgvpFw","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"• ↑ Bloqueo neuromuscular: Evitar coadministración con agentes bloqueadores neuromusculares.","guid":"KIZIGP_M_EdvotUoav1U9w","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"• ↓ Clindamicina con Rifampina (J Infect 2015;71:200): Monitorizar, ajustar dosis.","guid":"NiNj-bxzneWXCPTnbu49bQ","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"77","text":"• ↓ Clindamicina con Hierba de San Juan: Monitorizar, ajustar dosis.","guid":"6cDgTpzS4wX1nW1MoaS02A","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":80,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Infectología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Infectología","filename":"Clindamicina-2024","id":"map_1134","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Clindamicina-2024"}